@host = http://localhost:8080
@userId = 123

### 회원가입
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "Password123!",
    "username": "testuser",
    "name": "홍길동",
    "phoneNumber": "01012345678"
}

### 로그인
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "Password123!"
}

### 토큰 갱신
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{refreshToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 로그아웃
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 비밀번호 초기화 요청
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/password/reset
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com"
}

### 비밀번호 변경
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/auth/password/change
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "currentPassword": "Password123!",
    "newPassword": "NewPassword123!"
}

### 이메일 인증 요청
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/email/verify/request
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com"
}

### 이메일 인증 확인
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/email/verify/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "code": "123456"
}

### 인증 메일 재발송
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/email/verify/resend
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com"
}

### 인증 상태 확인
GET {{host}}/api/v1/auth/email/verify/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 사용자 목록 조회 (페이징, 검색, 정렬 포함)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/users?page=1&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc&search=test
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 특정 사용자 정보 조회
GET {{host}}/api/v1/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 사용자 정보 수정
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "updateduser",
    "name": "김길동",
    "phoneNumber": "01087654321",
    "address": {
        "street": "123 Main St",
        "city": "Seoul",
        "country": "South Korea",
        "postalCode": "12345"
    },
    "profileImage": "https://example.com/profile.jpg"
}

### 사용자 삭제
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 현재 로그인한 사용자 정보
GET {{host}}/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}